 INTRODUCTION
------------
This project is designed to make life easier for people who 
use Microsoft Windows. This application will help you keep
track of your hours, and overhours automatically, so you dont
miss out on any forgotten hours. It will record the time you
are logged in to windows, and also notify you when its lunch
and when its time to go home.

REQUIREMENTS
------------
This application is tested on the following systems:
* Microsoft Windows 7

INSTALLATION
------------
......

CONFIGURATION
-------------
To configure WorkTracker, double-click the icon in systemtray. 
You will then get access to a GUI (graphical user interface) 
that will explain what to do.

